'''ᱠᱩᱢᱟᱨ ᱥᱟᱝᱜᱟᱠᱟᱨᱟ''' (ᱡᱟᱱᱟᱢᱺ ᱒᱗ ᱚᱠᱴᱚᱵᱚᱨ ᱑᱙᱗᱗) ᱫᱚ ᱥᱨᱤᱞᱚᱝᱠᱟ ᱡᱮᱡᱟᱹᱛᱤᱭᱟᱹᱨᱤ ᱠᱨᱤᱠᱮᱴ ᱫᱚᱞ ᱨᱤᱱᱤᱡ ᱢᱤᱫ ᱠᱷᱮᱞᱣᱟᱟᱹᱨᱤ ᱠᱟᱱᱟᱭ ᱾ ᱡᱟᱦᱟᱸᱭ ᱫᱚ ᱢᱤᱫ ᱦᱩᱱᱟᱹᱨᱤᱭᱟᱹ ᱠᱨᱤᱠᱮᱴ ᱠᱷᱮᱞᱣᱟᱹᱨᱤ ᱞᱮᱠᱟᱛᱮ ᱠᱚ ᱢᱟᱱᱟᱣᱮ ᱠᱟᱱᱟ  ᱾<ref name="guardian">{{cite web|last1=Bull|first1=Andy|title=Kumar Sangakkara deserves to stand with modern cricket's four great peaks|url=http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2014/feb/25/the-spin-kumar-sangakkara|publisher=The Guardian|accessdate=13 November 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Fidel|first1=Andrew|title=Bangladesh v SL, 2nd Test, Chittagong, 2nd day February 5, 2014 The case for Sangakkara's all-time greatness|url=http://www.espncricinfo.com/bangladesh-v-sri-lanka-2013-14/content/story/716635.html|publisher=ESPNcricinfo|accessdate=13 November 2016}}</ref> ᱥᱟᱝᱜᱟᱠᱟᱨᱟ ᱫᱤᱱᱟᱜ (one-day) ᱢᱮᱪ ᱨᱮ ᱧᱩᱛᱩᱢᱟᱱᱤᱡ ᱵᱮᱴᱥᱢᱮᱱ ᱞᱮᱠᱟᱛᱮ ᱞᱮᱠᱷᱟᱜ ᱠᱟᱱ ᱵᱮᱲᱟ ᱨᱮ, ᱥᱨᱤᱞᱚᱝᱠᱟ ᱡᱮᱡᱟᱹᱛᱤᱭᱟᱹᱨᱤ ᱠᱨᱤᱠᱮᱴ ᱫᱚ ᱡᱤᱛᱠᱟᱹᱨ ᱚᱪᱚᱭᱤᱡ ᱢᱤᱫ ᱧᱩᱢᱟᱱ ᱢᱮᱪ-ᱡᱤᱛᱠᱟᱹᱨᱤᱭᱟᱹ ᱠᱷᱮᱞᱣᱟᱹᱨᱤ ᱢᱩᱸᱫᱽ ᱨᱮ ᱞᱮᱠᱷᱟᱜ ᱠᱟᱱᱟᱭ ᱾ ᱢᱚᱦᱮᱞᱟ ᱡᱚᱭᱵᱚᱨᱫᱷᱚᱱ ᱥᱟᱶ ᱥᱟᱝᱜᱟᱠᱟᱨᱟ ᱡᱮᱡᱟᱹᱛᱤᱭᱟᱹᱨᱤ ᱛᱷᱚᱠ ᱟᱹᱰᱤᱜᱟᱱ ᱨᱮᱠᱚᱨᱰ ᱠᱤᱱ ᱵᱮᱱᱟᱣ ᱟᱠᱟᱫᱼᱟ ᱾<ref name="guardian"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.espncricinfo.com/bangladesh-v-sri-lanka-2013-14/content/story/716635.html|title=The case for Kumar Sangakkara's all-time greatness -  Cricket  - ESPN Cricinfo|work=Cricinfo}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.icc-cricket.com/cricket-world-cup/news/2015/features-and-specials/87017/de-villiers-v-sangakkara-the-two-best-batsman-in-the-world|title=De Villiers v Sangakkara; the two best batsman in the World?|work=icc-cricket.com}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dnaindia.com/sport/comment-kumar-sangakkara-is-a-modern-test-great-who-never-gets-his-due-2049668|title=Kumar Sangakkara is a modern Test great who never gets his due|date=13 November 2016|work=dna}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sportskeeda.com/cricket/kumar-sangakkara-one-greatest-test-batsmen|title=Why Kumar Sangakkara is one of the greatest Test batsmen of all time|author=Theviyanthan Krishnamohan|date=13 November 2016|work=sportskeeda.com}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cricket.com.au/news/kumar-sangakkara-don-bradman-best/2014-06-15|title=The best batsman since Bradman|work=cricket.com.au}}</ref>

